Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:45.79,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It's tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:53.38,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,It's tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:06.18,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:11.48,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You've finally come home but all you do is dilly-dally around the house and skip school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.83,0:02:14.96,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone. I'll clean up on my own, so just go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:15.86,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:21.51,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,She's so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.55,0:02:24.76,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:27.16,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:31.12,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:32.85,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:35.69,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Poppo wants to meet up to make the final arrangements tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:36.89,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:38.22,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.51,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:44.10,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's meet up in front of the subway station...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:48.29,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, is Tsurumi still the same as always?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:51.36,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,She acts like she's the only one who understands you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:55.26,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,He's 181 cm tall and weighs 68 kilos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:56.73,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,His favorite food is a bean paste pastry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:02:59.28,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,His hobby is cross-dressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.90,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Cross-dressing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:04.92,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Wait Tsurumi, we still haven't asked what we wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:09.43,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:11.42,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:14.25,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You agreed not to talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:14.91,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It could really affect...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:15.54,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:25.36,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Tsurumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:28.56,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:32.06,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start our grand preparations for Menma's ascent to heaven tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:34.10,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make some decorations, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:35.77,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make flowers out of tissues!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:43.46,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,You're the guest of honor. Why are you getting involved in the preparations?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:45.22,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.24,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,That looks good, Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:52.05,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't space out Jintan. Make a garbage can out of those papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:54.58,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...? Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:55.42,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,A garbage can?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:59.25,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Back in the day I was a little dork.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:03.09,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I acted like an idiot so people would pay attention to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:07.60,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,But Jintan and everyone else became my friends, and in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:11.81,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Even though all I could do was watch everyone else from the sidelines...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:15.27,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,All I could do was watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:17.86,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Poppo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:22.70,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's why I'm taking care of everything this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:25.00,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you off in style, Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:26.20,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:29.27,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You're so nice, Poppo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:32.10,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:35.21,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:39.87,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,How much will those kids torment me before they're satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.22,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,How much...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:42.66,Default,Son,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.19,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:46.55,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that, Saa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:48.14,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:51.96,Default,Son,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even know how tall I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:55.87,Default,Son,0000,0000,0000,,I've grown a lot this past year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:16.43,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been lonesome, for both you and Satoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:22.16,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can forget about Meiko, and that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:25.10,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But I think we're all lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:29.71,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You, Satoshi, and myself, the three of us are together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:43.79,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what'll happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:46.28,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You mean if they launch the fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:48.84,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,If Menma disappears...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:51.55,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I used to think about it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:57.83,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,If Menma disappeared, Jintan and I would be able to get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:02.21,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:09.37,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,When Menma really disappeared, Jintan and I only became more distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:16.65,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,We've grown closer again, but that's only because Menma came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:19.30,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's something to be grateful for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:20.35,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:21.25,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:24.20,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tsurumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:25.53,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.24,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to the secret base today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:28.34,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:29.85,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,You're with Anjou, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:30.83,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.94,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:33.95,Default,Tusur,0000,0000,0000,,You coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:39.63,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:44.15,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,You pushed so hard for making her go to heaven, but now that it really comes down to it you're afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:45.23,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:47.08,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,It's really pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:51.80,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,You're afraid, so you run away from Menma and stay with Anjou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:54.85,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know you're not the only one who's miserable, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:07:00.89,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered about that time when Menma called us.  {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.36,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,About what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:06.08,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to ask us to do something for Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:12.85,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? What did Tsuruko say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:14.80,Default,Tusur,0000,0000,0000,,I have a request for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:18.65,Default,Tusur,0000,0000,0000,,It's something only you can do, Anaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:29.64,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:32.02,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, I'll see them tomorrow anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.11,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:35.72,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go call them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:37.43,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Poppo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.90,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Good job setting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:42.73,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:45.39,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I expected no less from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:46.65,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,And I brought juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:50.77,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Yukiatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:52.00,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,It's a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:53.10,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I believed in you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:55.20,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Party, party!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:55.20,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:58.20,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:01.05,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I love this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.05,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,So they've all shown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:02.14,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:03.30,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:08.64,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like the end is drawing closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:15.31,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem. We, the founders of the Super Peace Busters, together with Menma...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:16.84,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Skip the introductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:17.75,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:21.50,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, please come forward Menma, our guest of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.52,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:30.71,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,And then this!
