Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.00,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,It's all red!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:57.16,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I hate spicy stuff because it hurts.
