Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:11.68,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,This is supposed to be our final rally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:13.40,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We've all come together, so let's do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:14.85,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.86,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of game did you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.06,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:22.08,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,How about we go through that day again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:23.79,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:29.04,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's recreate how we met here on that day.
