Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.70,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw around! What do you want to accomplish by...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:37.26,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Anaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:46.73,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:47.44,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:51.86,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,You like Menma, don't you?
