Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:33.85,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:37.67,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Menma, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:41.12,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,If you run away now it'll all be the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:57.84,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Menma didn't make a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:02.85,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,She just let out a torrent of tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:14.19,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying already. It's shameful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:16.43,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a disgrace either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:19.71,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's an idea Yukiatsu instilled in you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:25.76,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Let's not do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:32.67,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I already know what he would have answered that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:36.15,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You'll stay lost without resolving anything even after Menma goes to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:38.64,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You'll keep losing to a Menma that shouldn't even be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.90,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you fine with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.32,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,You can't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:50.99,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,How it feels like to never have the person you like take notice of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:52.14,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,I do understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:55.10,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Because I like Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:12:02.01,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu has always been chasing after Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:06.11,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only side of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:08.08,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:10.80,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about 'never'.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:13.33,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Once Menma goes to heaven, Yadomi will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:14.01,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:19.89,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,But Yukiatsu definitely won't choose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:25.01,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Because even if Menma goes to heaven, you're the replacement for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:26.93,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:31.22,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the way it is! A replacement? Yukiatsu doesn't think of me that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:35.10,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, no matter how rough it is for me I'd never date Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:40.45,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,I like Jintan! I'm not some replacement!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:45.58,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, there's no replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:49.14,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we have to make Menma go to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:03.17,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.89,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I really put you on the spot there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:07.01,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Poppo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:12.59,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that everything seemed to wind back in time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:14.67,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Wind back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:16.85,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:18.04,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Is what you said earlier true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:19.35,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:21.75,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It... it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:25.24,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I like you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:30.12,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,When I said I liked you, it's not just the kind of liking between friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:34.53,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I know. It's the kind of liking that means you want to marry me right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:44.50,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,If I had kept growing up normally like this, I wonder if I would have become your bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:50.42,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it wasn't normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:51.11,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:55.85,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you just stay here instead of going to heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:57.81,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:03.52,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I've gone and said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:12.87,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:16.65,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You know about reincarnation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.35,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't go to heaven I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:22.23,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't be able to talk with everyone properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:25.79,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,But if I come back as a caterpillar...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:27.15,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,With everyone... properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:44.66,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,So Menma, when Jintan said he liked you, how did you answer him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:45.86,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:50.02,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to ask us to do something for Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:51.37,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I already know her answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:54.12,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Menma, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.86,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:59.40,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:04.96,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to heaven, okay Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:18.26,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Am I not enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:38.04,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Say Menma, do you know about reincarnation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.84,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Reincarnation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:47.09,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Even if your life ends, you can come back as a baby again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:53.74,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,And it may not be as a human. It could be as a baby kitten, or a baby flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:56.89,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's not scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.07,0:15:59.01,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.77,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But there's just one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:05.09,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Just one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:19.74,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just a little longer, auntie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:21.96,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's going to send up fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.95,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:35.20,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's start by outfitting the launch cylinder. {attaching weird decorations like strings or umbrellas that will come down when the firework cylinder reaches its apex}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:36.73,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Outfitting! {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:53.02,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:55.46,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:16:59.88,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What? Tsurumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:05.42,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute! You look like you did when you were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.28,0:17:07.25,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:08.74,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,I had a change of mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:13.47,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:13.88,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:17.80,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:19.33,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Grab a hold of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:21.67,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:23.71,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:28.73,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:32.28,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you really came.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:36.04,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:37.78,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:41.46,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that I caught a familiar scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:46.43,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You called Saa for me, Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:48.54,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:54.48,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:55.74,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:56.38,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:18:00.56,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,So this is really the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.71,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:05.07,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:11.09,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine like this right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:16.46,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Our interests are the same as Menma's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.91,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure she goes to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:22.52,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,But right now I can still stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:23.87,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yadomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:27.53,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Menma must be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:29.13,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:33.46,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let him stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:37.72,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I can stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:41.32,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I can stop her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:42.76,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:48.66,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.39,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:51.99,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:53.80,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:54.89,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.89,0:18:57.55,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You're so strong, Saa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:18:59.91,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yadomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:13.68,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Now all that's left is the launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:15.17,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,This was a job well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:19.19,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, does anyone have any last words or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:20.55,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Her brother is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.27,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:24.93,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just let it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:28.38,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,It was really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:30.37,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:31.10,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Poppo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.35,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,You go too, Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:47.43,Default,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this thing going. If it gets too late, it'll bother the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:49.47,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:50.62,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:04.09,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Is this all right? I can still stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:14.36,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I can stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:20.15,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:34.79,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,The firework went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:02.91,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! A flower blossomed in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:04.27,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:08.28,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:10.99,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:13.07,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is she there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:15.50,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is she still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:16.49,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:18.44,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the fireworks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:19.66,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:19.66,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? {couldn't make this out, so I made it up; can be ignored altogether}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:22.45,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:22.45,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help but think this at the time:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:26.09,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm glad you didn't disappear."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{TS, 07.35} Goodbye, Menma
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{TS, 08.32}        Thank you for doing this for me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{TS, 08.35}        I'm going to heaven tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{TS, 08.43}        I want to be friends with everyone until the very end. Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{TS, 08.56}        Super Peace Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,{TS, 11.07}        Fireworks
